284
00:16:28,971 --> 00:16:30,071
Ya!

285
00:16:30,071 --> 00:16:31,871
Benar kan, Dokter?

286
00:16:31,871 --> 00:16:33,971
Ya.

287
00:16:33,971 --> 00:16:39,171
