324
00:18:39,471 --> 00:18:42,771
Reaksi luminol, itu juga buktinya

325
00:18:42,771 --> 00:18:45,271
bahwa dia menyentuh darah Tn. Ushigome.

326
00:18:45,271 --> 00:18:46,371
Hei, Shoko!

327
00:18:46,371 --> 00:18:48,671
Apa kau akan diam saja?

328
00:18:48,671 --> 00:18:50,371
